Accum data into database during phase 1 and 2
	atParagraph
	speakerName
	speakerNumber
	explicit

Phase 3

receive command into reprocess.php
	bookNo, atParagraph, toName
read accum data for atParagraph
determine toNumber of toName
while no explicit speaker seen, process paragraph, whether matching or not
	read TTS for paragraph
	set speakerNumber to toNumber when === accum speakerNumber
		may occur multiple times
	write TTS for paragraph
	read next accum data


